{"tid":1738750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實男仔比人性騷擾/非禮先最慘","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T02:19:18.000Z","uid":302151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a091fff453545473f82c0dba507b28b149bc9ca","tid":1738750,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"成日係街比啲廢老抽水 <br />\n你係女既都話有人幫有人可憐你<br />\n你係男既你試下當街同人講你比個廢老非禮? <br />\n成班圍住笑你都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲廢老又唔撚要面既 當街屌番你轉頭 打鳩埋你都仲得<br />\n<br />\n想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 說好的男女平等呢<br />\n我真係好憎呢啲 對女仔做就唔得 對男仔做就好似冇所謂既事<br />\n點解我成日出街都要比廢老抽水呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我出個街都要搞到咁唔開心"},{"pid":"12e56a3031e2d13b234b7922ab906afd4e961c72","tid":1738750,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"你係咪又矮又毒"},{"pid":"a4193926e749b262b4289f4944158da92bd0687e","tid":1738750,"uid":302151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"12e56a3031e2d13b234b7922ab906afd4e961c72","tid":1738750,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"你係咪又矮又毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"即刻出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c176149f108ab2b6f4f60fafe48630e8d92106","tid":1738750,"uid":214192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:48:56.000Z"